  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Investing in entrepreneurial youth</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims at introducing entrepreneurship into the education system of the Democratic Republic of Congo,  with a view to promote entrepreneurial youth and to contribute to the reform of the education system to improve the preparation of the predominantly young population for their careers. The project will introduce an Entrepreneurship Curriculum Programme  (ECP) to support the development of entrepreneurial culture and skills, and technical thinking. Entrepreneurship is introduced as a subject in general secondary schools, TVET, non-formal education and higher education.</narrative>
  </description>
